            <p align="left"><strong>Above:</strong> Bethel Chapel, Flushdyke (Map 24).</p>
            <p align="center"><a href="pages/flushdyke_burdekins.html" target="_blank"><img src="images/flushdyke_burdekins_small.jpg" alt="Burdekin's Basket Works, Flushdyke" width="499" height="364" border="0"></a> </p>
